can someone describe three main characters of harry potter in detail harry potter is a black haired green eyed bespeckled orphan he lives with his aunt petunia dursley his mother's sister his uncle vernon dursley and his cousin dudley dursley his parents were killed by lord voldemort the most evil wizard of his time nobody has ever survived the killing curse except for harry all harry has to show this is a lightning bolt shaped scar he is famous for the downfall of lord voldemort because of this harry is called the boy who lived because he survived the killing curse he has a knack for getting into trouble and seeing things others cannot like the golden snitch in quidditch harry can speak parseltongue the language of snakes his mother was born into a muggle family and his father was a pureblood making him halfblood he has best friends ron and hermione ron weasley is a th child of in the family of weasleys all of his family has flaming bright red hair ron is not stupid but lazy and brings humor into the trio of friends he feels overshadowed by his family his oldest brothers all being notorious for something in hogwarts being a prefect head boy and a quidditch playing star his other brothers fred and george are hilarious and are popular for being class clowns he is tall gangly and has blue eyes he is a pureblood ron is in love with hermione hermione granger is the brains of the bunch she was born into a family of muggles non magical folk however she is the smartest student in the year at hogwarts she has bushy brown hair and brown eyes without her the other two could not have done half of their homework or gotten through tasks without her because often she has the answer to what they are looking for she is in love with ron Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban (film) Hogwarts subjects Draco Malfoy Minor Harry Potter Beasts Hogwarts Houses Severus Snape Albus Dumbledore Minor Slytherins Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone (video game) Rubeus Hagrid Harry Potter 